Oh no! It looks like your game crashed.

Follow these steps to get things back up and running!

\n\t\t

Launch the game again.

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t\t\t

If this is the first time the game has crashed, close this page and launch the game again. Sometimes these things just happen!

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t
\n \n
\n\t\t\t

2

\n\t\t\t

Check your antivirus software.

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t\t\t

Lately we've been getting many reports of crashes caused by antivirus and anti-malware software blocking the game from either reading its files or saving to its save directory. Newer versions of Windows 10 will even sometimes block programs from saving to the My Documents folder. If you're running an antivirus or anti-malware program, please make sure that it's not the culprit by checking that program's logs and/or temporarily disabling it.

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t
\n \n\t\t
\n\t\t\t

3

\n\t\t\t

Update your video drivers and restart your computer.

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t\t\t

Another thing to try before contacting us is to update your video drivers. Find your video card manufacturer in the list below, and then click either the link to the manual or automatic driver download page. After updating your drivers, be sure to restart your computer!

\n\t\t\t

If all else fails, ask Zach!

\n\t\t\t
\n\t\t\t\t

If the steps above haven't solved the problem, use the form below to email Zach. Fill in your email address in the 'from' field and then briefly describe what you were doing when the game crashed. The email will automatically include information about the crash, your system, and your save file.

To export a Redshift solution, open the solution's context menu and click the "export" button. A PNG image of a disc that _contains the solution's data_ will be saved to your desktop.

You can share these images with other players via email, social networks, or any other file transfer method.

Chinese: 你将会看到在一些小票，请将它们的内容录入电脑，以便记账和报销。为忙碌的主管节省一两分钟时间

English: You will comb over patent filings for potential examples of prior art in order to provide important information for patent litigation. Don’t worry about understanding the technical terminology— any match is a good one!
VISUAL INSPECTION OF BEEF AND PORK

You will monitor a networked digital camera inside a meat processing facility, keeping a keen eye out for mishandling, spoiled or rotten products, and other issues. Make a contribution to food safety and public health!

You will browse a large database of corporate personnel records. Some of the entries are slightly modified duplicates created with the intent to defraud the corporation. Identify the duplicate entries and send them packing!

You will be shown images of various pieces of refuse as they are conveyed along a track at a waste processing facility. Categorize these objects as Paper, Glass, Metal, or Rubber. By helping to sort our trash, you make non-toxic water possible!

Number cards are stacked by *alternating color* and *decreasing value*,\nand can be moved together as a stack of any size.
Spanish: Las cartas de número se apilan por *color alternante* y *valor decreciente*,\ny pueden moverse juntas como una pila de cuelquier tamaño.
Chinese: 数字牌按照 *交替花色* 和 *从大到小* 的规则来堆叠，\n任意大小的牌堆都可以一起移动。

English: Face cards are stacked *by suit* in *any order*, and can also be moved as a stack. However, a completed stack of face cards placed directly on the board will become immovable.
Spanish: Las cartas de figura se apilan *por palo* en *cualquier orden*, y también se pueden mover como pila. Sin embargo, una pila completa, puesta directamente sobre la mesa, se volverá inamovible.
Chinese: 花面牌安装 *同花色* 和 *不论次序* 的规则来堆叠并移动。但是，一堆完整的花面牌放上桌板后 ，将无法移动。

English: To win, sort the dealt cards into four completed stacks of number cards\nand four completed stacks of face cards.
Spanish: Para ganar, ordena las cartas repartidas en cuatro pilas completas de número\ny cuatro pilas completas de figuras.
Chinese: 要赢得游戏，请排好四叠数字牌和四叠花面牌。

English: The *free cell* in the top-right corner of the board can store a single card of any type.
Spanish: La *celda libre* en la esquina superior derecha puede guardar una sola carta de cualoquier tipo.
Chinese: 右上角的*自由格*可以存储任何类型的单张牌。
